{"id":7885,"date":"2012-10-10T14:39:24","date_gmt":"2012-10-10T18:39:24","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.dailyhadithonline.com\/?p=7885"},"modified":"2025-03-08T12:50:22","modified_gmt":"2025-03-08T08:50:22","slug":"prophet-hawariyyun-sahabah","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/10\/prophet-hawariyyun-sahabah\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Prophets: Every Prophet has followers defending his Sunnah"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201c<strong>Allah did not send any Prophet to the nations before me but that he was given disciples and companions who held to his tradition and followed his command. Then, after them came their successors, who said what they did not practice and who practiced what they were not commanded. He who strove against them with his hand was a believer, and he who strove against them with his tongue was a believer, and he who strove against them with his heart was a believer; after that there is not even a mustard seed of faith<\/strong>.&#8221;<\/p>\n<p>Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 50<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <em><strong>Sahih<\/strong> <\/em>(authentic) according to Muslim<\/p>\n<p align=\"right\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0633\u0652\u0639\u064f\u0648\u062f\u064d \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0645\u064e\u0627 \u0645\u0650\u0646\u0652 \u0646\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u064d\u0651 \u0628\u064e\u0639\u064e\u062b\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0